- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on identifying and refactoring design smells in software systems. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of event-driven programming in UIs. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper deals with UI design and user interactions. 
- cs.SD (Software Development) is relevant as the paper discusses software design and refactoring. 
- cs.UI (User Interfaces) is relevant as the paper specifically deals with UI design smells and their detection.
